Inspirations:
  - berry
  - bspwm (xcb trickery and functions, namely check_connection)
  - sowm
  - swm (xcb)
  - xwm (started as a fork)
  - windowchef (for xcb/randr)

Dependencies:
  - GNU make
  - GCC
  - libxcb-devel
  - xcb-util-keysyms-devel
  - libX11-devel (needed for configuration)

